    "Finally, cross-scale feature fusion allows for feature complementation and improvement, which improves feature quality and expressive ability.",
    "Inspired by literature 41, we replace the detection head of the original network with a decoupling head [42] [43] [44].",
    "The decoupling head assigns classification and regression tasks to distinct network branches and uses different weight values.",
    "This can improve detection performance by better distinguishing the foreground and background in low-light settings.",
